    "name": "Hotel Tentrem Yogyakarta",
    "detail": "My stay in the hotel with my family for vacation is fantastic. The staff are friendly, professional and prompt in their service. The food in the hotel restaurant are nice. We like the swimming pool and the children playroom the most. Only one bad logistic issue that does not reflect the hotel's culture and image. Everything in the hotel is spick and span, except for the old iron and ironing board when I needed it to iron my clothes. In fact I have to ask for a second time before they gave it to me. The reason being they does not have enough old iron to lend it to me and I have to be put on the waiting list. After much pressing before they deliver almost immediately. But fortunately, the staff still bother to rectify my problem. Overall, I would recommend this as the best hotel in Yogyakarta.",
